				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">DPS of the boulder is much bigger than Epic with weapons (which is the very best pet in Ldon normal). He hits for 300/400.
<br />
prepare 3 hot keys :
<br />
1/ mezz
<br />
2/ sinia
<br />
3/ charm
<br />

<br />
and it's all done.
<br />
I've been told a very high charisma can help, mine is 60, and it's OK.
<br />
.
<br />
TIPS :
<br />
1/ when charm breaks, mob hits you, of course. If you are in a corner, he will not interrupt your mezz. 
<br />
2/ When you are not casting, let pet be your target. hitting F1 twice does not work when you are casting, too bad !
<br />
3/ to retarget pet faster, I use some hot keys :
<br />
4) /assist %t
<br />
5) /pet attack 
<br />

<br />
then F4 (tank or puller) 4 5 sends pet
<br />
Alt 1 (destroy sumon)
<br />
F1 F1 when I can
<br />

<br />
I also shrink pet : it is easier to click on a shrunk pet if charm broke while casting, this is also why I prefer fighting on a upper position (sand)
<br />

<br />
NO BO5 nor WEAPONS, really too dangerous for me ! I do it in BOT, not in LDON? bc mob is really too close to me, I am never fully buffed in there, then I am around 4K, not enough to survive a speedy mob if first mezz fails.<br />_________________<br /><IMG SRC="http://www.ikebana-toulouse.com/citation/signatc.jpg" WIDTH="266" HEIGHT="96" ISMAP USEMAP="#signatc"><MAP NAME="signatc"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" HREF="http://www.ikebana-toulouse.com"COORDS="4,71,50,97"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" HREF="http://vof.student.utwente.nl" COORDS="9,40,153,69"><AREA SHAPE="CIRCLE" HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=159910" COORDS="205,53,40"></MAP><BR><BR><FONT COLOR="#ef56d0">BIRD for my stats; SouthWest flower for IKEBANA;<BR>GUILD NAME for VOF site</FONT></span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by Ailees on Tue Jan 06, 2004 2:27 pm; edited 1 time in total</span></td>
