				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">In LDoN I will charm when I have a guild enchie or bard with me whom I know I can trust. Then I grab the meanest thing I can charm and BO5 + muzzle + dual proc weapon him and go to town.
<br />

<br />
The DPS is awesome and the bard or ench will bring him under control when you lose it for the few brief seconds you need to get charm back on. Blessing of Reverence is also a good investment in buffs as always.
<br />

<br />
If I don't have a reliable partner I tend to use Jabober and concentrate on maximising my nuke DPS.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=86257" target="_blank" class="postlink">Zaniel Stormseeker</a>
