				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The risk of one charm breaking is negligable with five other people in the group. The risk of two broken charms, while a low-probablility, has the outcome of more than likely wiping the group should it happen. 
<br />

<br />
Since with even without a charmed pet we can turn Normals faster than refresh allows, and Hards in under an hour, to me, the slight slight gains in speed are not worth the risk.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=568700" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Itchyban of Veeshan</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
