				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If your the only reliable charmer/mezzer in your group its safe to give him weapons and mask since the incrased DPS is minial and the Mezz spell channels very nicely. BO5 should really only be used if you have a reliable back up partner.
<br />

<br />
As far as chanters go... I trust me guild chanters and we back eachother up. Two cracked out rock piles make for a fast LDoN. best we did was a collect 30 normal with about 70 minutes remain with me, chanter, two beasties, warrior, and cleric. 90% of the pulling involed me and the chanter just rushing the room <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
A BO5 rubble pile will also own most of the LDoN named.<br />_________________<br />Mordican - Arch Mage of Infinite Visions
<br />
Maelin Starphyre Server
<br />

