Color Cloud and Word of Morell = teh win. The enchies I'm doing this with can handle 4 adds + 2 broken charms if they have to. An enchanter who's a heavy user of pets soon becomes an amazing expert in controlling these sorts of situations. I just need to run my pet over near the enchie to take advantage of his PBAEO stun and then I recharm, no mez or other CC required from the enchie.
<br />

<br />
Besides, worst case scenario I can run my ex-charm pet around the room for 10 seconds whilst he takes care of the rest. If I'm really desperate then our healer should be able to keep me up while I try to channel 4-5 times.
<br />

<br />
Besides in normal L65 LDoN adventures there shouldn't really be any mezzing of adds needed, the name of the game is bulldoze.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=86257" target="_blank" class="postlink">Zaniel Stormseeker</a>
<br />
Arch Convoker of <a href="http://www.afflictionguild.com" target="_blank" class="postlink">Affliction</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
